And here I came
in my Easter best.

6
00:01:26.541 --> 00:01:28.666
What the fuck is that thing?

7
00:01:28.750 --> 00:01:30.458
It's a rabbit?

8
00:01:30.541 --> 00:01:32.291
I don't care what
it is. Kill it.

9
00:01:32.375 --> 00:01:33.583
Oh.

10
